title: What Would You Do  (5/23/2014)
description:
What Would You Do?  (5/23/2014) 

newest episode  after there long break
cool hidden camera show to see how people react to hard situations

was on hulu but u need a provider login so i used my xfinity on demand

the old episodes are there if u want to see them 
if ur outside of usa u can google new ways to still watch 


In the series, actors act out scenes of conflict or illegal activity in public settings while hidden cameras videotape the scene, and the focus is on whether or not bystanders intervene, and how. Variations are also usually included, such as changing the genders, the races or the clothing of the actors performing the scene, to see if bystanders react differently.
